HEADWORD: Flatboat
<hw>Flat"boat`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A boat with a flat
bottom and square ends; -- used for the transportation of bulky freight,
especially in shallow waters.</def>⟦br⟧
